    "rationale": "The assessment team concludes that the CFD hemolysis model provides sufficient credibility evidence to support the VAD submission decision. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification was completed and the majority of credibility factors were assessed. Remaining gaps are considered manageable given the conservative nature of the power-law hemolysis model. Medium assurance level is declared consistent with partial factor completion across all 13 ASME V&V 40 factors.",
